messages.message:
Not sure if this is helpful but at least one of the reasons clients-factory-lib has been getting imported into api-server for a while is the following line of dependencies: api server -> jobs-lib -> flow-lib -> clients-factory-lib

I’m heading out for a bike ride now and will be back online later this afternoon and tonight to do a bunch of testing and associated bug fixing on refiner 5 before the code cut.

hey! considering things are working without any dockerfile updates, I'm assuming these changes were not introduced in this release? if so, then let's punt the discussion/investigation to after this release because we are still busy fixing last minute bugs with Refiner 5

:thumbsup_all: I don’t think we need to necessarily make a decision in this release.  The boto deps might be getting pulled in due to SQSClient deps.

I’ll set up some time next week to chat through the next steps — we should make a decision one way or the other on this front.
